<section style="background:var(--color-base, #f2ead4); padding:80px 24px;">
  <div style="max-width:800px; margin:0 auto;">
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.75rem; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:0.15em; text-transform:uppercase; color:#b98229; margin-bottom:1rem;">Local Expertise</p>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:clamp(1.8rem, 3.5vw, 2.8rem); font-weight:300; line-height:1.2; color:#191817; margin-bottom:1.75rem;">Generous blocks and a genuine family neighbourhood.</h2>
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:1rem; font-weight:300; line-height:1.8; color:#4a4540; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
      McDowall is one of north Brisbane's most settled family suburbs, sitting roughly twelve kilometres from the CBD between Kedron Brook and the Samford Road corridor. It offers land content that inner-north buyers can no longer access at the same price point, and the suburb attracts families who have done serious market comparisons before arriving here with conviction.
    </p>
<!-- APPRAISAL FORM -->
