<!-- END APPRAISAL FORM -->
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:1rem; font-weight:300; line-height:1.8; color:#4a4540; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
      I know this part of Brisbane well. I understand why buyers choose McDowall over Stafford Heights or Everton Park, what they are willing to pay for land and position, and how to structure a campaign that attracts that buyer profile. That local understanding is the foundation of every result I achieve here.
    </p>
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:1rem; font-weight:300; line-height:1.8; color:#4a4540; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
      McDowall's comparative advantage is its blocks. Many properties in the suburb sit on 600 to 800 square metre sites, with usable outdoor space that is difficult to source in tighter northern suburbs at the same price level. The Kedron Brook linear parkway forms the suburb's southern boundary, giving residents access to cycling and walking trails without the traffic exposure of a main road position. Buyers relocating from Ashgrove, Gaythorne or Mitchelton consistently find that McDowall delivers better land value at a practical trade-off in commute time. The internal streets are quiet and well-established, and the proportion of long-term owner-occupiers is high, which sustains the settled character that family buyers pay a premium for.
    </p>
    <div style="display:flex; gap:1.5rem; flex-wrap:wrap;">
      <div style="flex:1; min-width:200px; background:#fff; padding:1.75rem; border-left:3px solid #b98229;">
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.1rem; font-weight:400; color:#191817; margin-bottom:0.4rem;">McDowall Specialist</p>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:300; color:#6b6560;">North Brisbane</p>
      </div>
      <div style="flex:1; min-width:200px; background:#fff; padding:1.75rem; border-left:3px solid #b98229;">
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.1rem; font-weight:400; color:#191817; margin-bottom:0.4rem;">Generous Block Sizes</p>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:300; color:#6b6560;">Strong family buyer demand</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p style="font-size:0.82rem;color:#78716c;margin-top:2rem;">Also selling in: <a href="/suburbs/stafford-heights" style="color:#b98229;">Stafford Heights</a>, <a href="/suburbs/everton-park" style="color:#b98229;">Everton Park</a>, <a href="/suburbs/mitchelton" style="color:#b98229;">Mitchelton</a>.</p>
  </div>
</section>

